eu.amidst.core.datastream

Class DataOnMemoryListContainer<E extends DataInstance>

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.core.datastream.DataOnMemoryListContainer<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataOnMemory<E>, DataStream<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class DataOnMemoryListContainer<E extends DataInstance>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataOnMemory<E>
    This class implements a DataOnMemory interface. It stores all the DataInstance objects in a List.
